2-0354" class="document">TJs letter of 30 Aug. 1785</a>. Enclosure: Copy of <a href="default.xqy?keys=TSJN-print-01-08-02-0260" class="document">John Paul Jones to TJ, 29 July 1785.</a></p></div>
